  "categorySlug": "data-more-videos",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Unstrukturierte Daten: Ein unterschätztes Risiko mit haftungsrechtlichen Folgen</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Einmal mit Liebe gesagt: Viele reden über Datenschutz, aber wenige machen wirklich etwas dafür!</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>Schaut Euch bitte einfach dieses Video an. Danach wisst Ihr, dass ein Risiko in Euren Daten schlummert, das Euch bis zu 172 € pro Datei kosten kann. Dann wisst Ihr, das Mitarbeiter aufräumen müssen, es aber nicht tun. Dann kennt Ihr die Statistiken, welche kritischen Daten wo eigentlich bei Euch liegen.</p>\n<p>Und wenn Ihr bis zum Schluss des Videos durchhaltet, dann zeige ich Euch, wie Ihr wirklich aufräumen könnt.</p>\n<div class=\"hs-video-widget\" data-hsv-embed-id=\"ecb346bf-a43a-42f4-9fb8-9cb777a824ed\">\n  <div class=\"hs-video-container\" style=\"max-width: 688px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <div class=\"hs-video-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; height: 0; padding-bottom: 56.25%\">\n      <iframe data-hsv-src=\"https://play.hubspotvideo.com/v/4381120/id/184656098157\" referrerpolicy=\"origin\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen;\" style=\"position: absolute !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; left: 0; top: 0; border: 0 none; pointer-events: initial\" title=\"HubSpot Video\" loading=\"lazy\" data-hsv-id=\"184656098157\" data-hsv-style=\"\" data-hsv-width=\"688\" data-hsv-height=\"387\" data-hsv-autoplay=\"false\" data-hsv-loop=\"false\" data-hsv-muted=\"false\" data-hsv-hidden-controls=\"false\" data-hsv-full-width=\"false\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
